Title: A Framework for Local Anonymity in the Internet  
Author: David M. Martin Jr. 
Date: 21st February 1998  
Address: 111 Cummington Street Boston, MA 02215  
Affiliation: Department of Computer Science  
Abstract: We describe and evaluate options for providing anonymous IP service, argue for the further investigation of local anonymity, and sketch a framework for the implementation of locally anonymous networks. 
